---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Legal Disclosure & Affiliates | TaxDebtWealthSuite"
  description="Important legal and financial disclosures regarding the use of our calculators and planning tools."
>
  <main class="flex-grow max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400 border border-rose-500/20 mb-4">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">Disclosure</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">1. Not Financial Advice</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400">
        The calculators, articles, and tools provided on TaxDebtWealthSuite are for <strong>educational and informational purposes only</strong>. They do not constitute professional financial, tax, legal, or investment advice. While we strive for mathematical perfection based on current tax codes, individual financial situations are complex and nuanced. You should always consult with a certified public accountant (CPA), fiduciary financial advisor, or legal counsel before making structural financial decisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">2. Accuracy of Calculations</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400">
        Our tools provide <em>estimates</em> based on the inputs you provide and standard tax brackets/formulas. They may not account for state/provincial taxes, local municipalities, alternative minimum taxes (AMT), phase-outs, or recent legislative changes that have not yet been codified. We make no warranties, express or implied, regarding the absolute accuracy of the results.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">3. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400">
        TaxDebtWealthSuite is a free service. To maintain our servers and continue developing free tools, we may participate in various affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn a commission if you click on or make a purchase via certain links on our site (such as links to brokerage accounts, tax software, or credit cards). 
        <br><br>
        However, our editorial integrity is paramount. We will never recommend a product we do not genuinely believe is useful, and our calculators are never skewed to favor an affiliate partner.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">4. Assumption of Risk</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400">
        Advanced financial strategies, such as using Securities-Based Lines of Credit (SBLOCs) or margin loans, carry significant risks including the total loss of capital via margin calls. By using our tools to model these strategies, you acknowledge that you are solely responsible for your financial decisions and the associated risks.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
